2) cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper discusses the design of a cloud radio access network (C-RAN) architecture, which falls under the domain of networking and internet architecture. 
3) cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper deals with the joint optimization of analog and digital components of a hybrid beamforming solution, which can be viewed as a control problem. 
4) cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper discusses the optimization of a downlink system, which is related to multimedia communication. 
5) cs.COM (Computers and Society) - This category is less likely, but the paper does touch upon the topic of energy efficiency, which can be viewed as a societal concern.
